{"id":966,"parent_id":964,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":966,"title":"Malachi 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mal.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The priests are reproved for not keeping their covenants and not teaching the people—The Jews are condemned for dealing treacherously with one another and with their wives."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.1","order":"02.40.002.63429"},["b","1"],"And now, O ye priests, this commandment",["i","is"],"for you."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.2","order":"02.40.002.63430"},["b","2"],"If ye will not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"hear"],", and if ye will not lay",["i","it"],"to heart, to give glory unto my name, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, I will even send a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"curse"],"upon you, and I will curse your blessings: yea, I have cursed them already, because ye do not lay",["i","it"],"to heart."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.3","order":"02.40.002.63431"},["b","3"],"Behold, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"corrupt"],"your seed, and spread dung upon your faces,",["i","even"],"the dung of your solemn feasts; and",["i","one"],"shall take you away with it."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.4","order":"02.40.002.63432"},["b","4"],"And ye shall know that I have sent this commandment unto you, that my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"covenant"],"might be with Levi, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.5","order":"02.40.002.63433"},["b","5"],"My",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"covenant"],"was with him of life and peace; and I gave them to him",["i","for"],"the fear wherewith he feared me, and was afraid before my name."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.6","order":"02.40.002.63434"},["b","6"],"The law of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"truth"],"was in his mouth, and iniquity was not found in his lips: he walked with me in peace and equity, and did",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"turn"],"many away from",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"iniquity"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.7","order":"02.40.002.63435"},["b","7"],"For the priest’s lips should keep",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"knowledge"],", and they should seek the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"law"],"at his mouth: for he",["i","is"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"messenger"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.8","order":"02.40.002.63436"},["b","8"],"But ye are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"departed"],"out of the way; ye have caused many to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"stumble"],"at the law; ye have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"corrupted"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"covenant"],"of Levi, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.9","order":"02.40.002.63437"},["b","9"],"Therefore have I also made you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"contemptible"],"and base before all the people, according as ye have not kept my ways, but have been partial in the law."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.10","order":"02.40.002.63438"},["b","10"],"Have we not all one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"father"],"? hath not one God",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"created"],"us? why do we deal treacherously every man against his brother, by",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"profaning"],"the covenant of our fathers?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.11","order":"02.40.002.63439"},["b","11"],"¶Judah hath dealt treacherously, and an abomination is committed in Israel and in Jerusalem; for Judah hath profaned the holiness of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"which he loved, and hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"married"],"the daughter of a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"strange god"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.12","order":"02.40.002.63440"},["b","12"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"cut off"],"the man that doeth this, the master and the scholar, out of the tabernacles of Jacob, and him that offereth an offering unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.13","order":"02.40.002.63441"},["b","13"],"And this have ye done again, covering the altar of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"with tears, with weeping, and with crying out, insomuch that he regardeth not the offering any more, or receiveth",["i","it"],"with good will at your hand."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.14","order":"02.40.002.63442"},["b","14"],"¶Yet ye say, Wherefore? Because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath been witness between thee and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wife"],"of thy youth, against whom thou hast dealt treacherously: yet",["i","is"],"she thy companion, and the wife of thy covenant."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.15","order":"02.40.002.63443"},["b","15"],"And did not he make",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"one"],"? Yet had he the residue of the spirit. And wherefore one? That he might seek a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"godly"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"seed"],". Therefore take heed to your spirit, and let none deal treacherously against the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"wife"],"of his youth."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.16","order":"02.40.002.63444"},["b","16"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the God of Israel, saith that he hateth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"putting away"],": for",["i","one"],"covereth violence with his garment, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts: therefore take heed to your spirit, that ye deal not treacherously."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.17","order":"02.40.002.63445"},["b","17"],"¶Ye have wearied the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"with your words. Yet ye say, Wherein have we wearied",["i","him?"],"When ye say, Every one that doeth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"evil"],["i","is"],"good in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and he delighteth in them; or, Where",["i","is"],"the God of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"judgment"],"?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.2a","order":"02.40.002.63446"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.15"},"Deut. 28:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.2b","order":"02.40.002.63448"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.3a","order":"02.40.002.63450"},["b","3a"],["span.small","OR"],"rebuke."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.4a","order":"02.40.002.63452"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-oath-and-covenant"},"TG Priesthood, Oath and Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.5a","order":"02.40.002.63454"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/25.12.11-13"},"Num. 25:12 (11–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.10"},"Isa. 54:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.6a","order":"02.40.002.63456"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.6b","order":"02.40.002.63458"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/66.1"},"D&C 66:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.6c","order":"02.40.002.63460"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.19.17-19"},"Hel. 5:19 (17–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.7a","order":"02.40.002.63462"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.15.14-15"},"D&C 90:15 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.99.99-100"},"107:99 (99–100)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/131.6"},"131:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.7b","order":"02.40.002.63464"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.26"},"Ezek. 7:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.7c","order":"02.40.002.63466"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teacher"},"TG Teacher"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.8a","order":"02.40.002.63468"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.26"},"Ezek. 22:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.8b","order":"02.40.002.63470"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.8.8-9"},"Mosiah 27:8 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.8c","order":"02.40.002.63472"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.17"},"1 Sam. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.8d","order":"02.40.002.63474"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/13.29"},"Neh. 13:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.9a","order":"02.40.002.63476"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.30"},"1 Sam. 2:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.10a","order":"02.40.002.63478"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.6"},"Eph. 4:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-the-father-elohim"},"TG God the Father, Elohim"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.10b","order":"02.40.002.63480"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/31.15"},"Job 31:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/17.26"},"Acts 17:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.24.22-24"},"D&C 76:24 (22–24)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-physical-creation-of"},"TG Man, Physical Creation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.10c","order":"02.40.002.63482"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/profanity"},"TG Profanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.11a","order":"02.40.002.63484"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-interfaith"},"TG Marriage, Interfaith"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.11b","order":"02.40.002.63486"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"TG Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.12a","order":"02.40.002.63488"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/excommunication"},"TG Excommunication"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.14a","order":"02.40.002.63490"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.6"},"Isa. 54:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-marry"},"TG Marriage, Marry"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.15a","order":"02.40.002.63492"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.15b","order":"02.40.002.63494"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/godliness"},"TG Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.15c","order":"02.40.002.63496"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.30"},"Jacob 2:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"15d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.15d","order":"02.40.002.63498"},["b","15d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-husbands"},"TG Marriage, Husbands"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.16a","order":"02.40.002.63500"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/divorce"},"TG Divorce"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.17a","order":"02.40.002.63502"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.16.7-8,16"},"2 Ne. 28:16 (7–8, 16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.17b","order":"02.40.002.63504"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.14.14-15"},"Mal. 3:14 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.22.16-22"},"2 Ne. 28:22 (16–22)"],"."]]}
